""SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Address], [t].[CreatedDate], [t].[Deleted], [t].[Email], [t].[EmailVerified], [t].[FamilyName], [t].[FullName], [t].[GivenName], [t].[IsActive], [t].[LangCode], [t].[LastActivity], [t].[LastChangePassword], [t].[MustChangePassword], [t].[Password], [t].[PhoneNumber], [t].[PhoneNumberVerified], [t].[Picture], [t].[Timeout], [t].[Timezone], [t].[UserName], [t].[UsergroupId], [t].[Id0], [t].[Description], [t].[IsActive0], [t].[IsDefault], [t].[IsRoot], [t].[Name], [t].[Priority], [t0].[RolesId], [t0].[UsersId], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Description], [t0].[IsDefault], [t0].[IsRoot], [t0].[Name], [t0].[Priority]

    SELECT TOP(2) [u].[Id], [u].[Address], [u].[CreatedDate], [u].[Deleted], [u].[Email], [u].[EmailVerified], [u].[FamilyName], [u].[FullName], [u].[GivenName], [u].[IsActive], [u].[LangCode], [u].[LastActivity], [u].[LastChangePassword], [u].[MustChangePassword], [u].[Password], [u].[PhoneNumber], [u].[PhoneNumberVerified], [u].[Picture], [u].[Timeout], [u].[Timezone], [u].[UserName], [u].[UsergroupId], [u0].[Id] AS [Id0], [u0].[Description], [u0].[IsActive] AS [IsActive0], [u0].[IsDefault], [u0].[IsRoot], [u0].[Name], [u0].[Priority]
